  'ZEND_FETCH_RW()', 'ZEND_CONCAT()', and 'ZEND_ASSIGN_CONCAT()' opcodes, and
  the 'ArrayObject::uasort' method, trigger memory corruption by causing a
  userspace interruption of an internal function or handler.");

